result.formatted_address: Hong Kong, Fanling, Pak Wo Rd, 88號73-80&83
result.name: 福滿庭酒家

reviews.text:
A relatively small place as a Chinese restaurant. Insufficient staff were noted during the visit as they were busy but polite.
Dim sum taste above average, although the baby pigeon is a bit salty but the texture of the meat are good.
Texture of stream rice roll with assorted meats and vegetable tasted great
Price is acceptable, location is a bit remote if ride on public transport.
Will try to have dinner there.
Dim sum tastes great and has reasonable price
Authentic Cantonese place, recommend the roast duck, served in heated plate .. tasty and not oily at all. Try everything, you won’t disappointed.

Very good food
The chef is keen on studying delicious dishes of good food for the customers.
Nice dim sum with the family.

result.adr_address: 香港粉嶺百和路88號73-80&83
result.name: 福滿庭酒家

reviews.text: 粉嶺花都廣塲,此店收費頗貴,茶錢,白飯㫮為$13,未算加一.侍應老邁,竟然話提唔清楚菜單編號,要我等重覆再講,奇聞!招呼ㄧ般,唔怪得晚市疏落,下不為例。
粉嶺花都廣場的福滿庭食品種類款式都算多，價錢尚算公道，地方比較細，往往都要等侯，晚飯小菜比較貴，碟頭都算足夠。
下午茶點心食品都OK,例如乳鸽味道算吾錯，晚飯小菜都幾好。價錢不算很貴。
出品都Ok，招呼就一般，價錢都吾貴。
D嘢好食，但是地方太細
